EU’s Almunia Says Bourse Deal to Face ‘Deep’ Probe, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-11T00:49:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/eu-s-almunia-says-bourse-deal-to-face-deep-probe-ft-reports.html
  Joaquin Almunia , European
competition commissioner, said the proposed merger between
Deutsche Boerse AG and  NYSE Euronext (NYX)  is a “complex case” that
is likely to undergo a “deep investigation,” the Financial
Times reported, citing a speech in Brussels on March 9.  To contact the reporter on this story:
